family that Lima Barreto.

01:05:45.490 --> 01:05:49.490
And Mashado Dajasheesh is not
sure that he was against --

01:05:49.490 --> 01:05:54.030
that he was a person that did
not -- was against slave system.

01:05:54.030 --> 01:05:58.920
He was. As a public servant
he frequently used to give --

01:05:58.920 --> 01:06:03.520
used to charge the owner
-- the slave owners.

01:06:03.520 --> 01:06:05.460
But at the same time
in this situation,

01:06:05.460 --> 01:06:10.540
very very very beautiful
a person,

01:06:10.540 --> 01:06:15.910
because one can't understand
the difference of being a critic

01:06:15.910 --> 01:06:19.960
or experiencing this
kind of life.

01:06:19.960 --> 01:06:21.260
&gt;&gt; Bryan McCann: Right.

