No? And Clara was a mulatto.

01:07:28.870 --> 01:07:31.170
He describes her as a mulatto.

01:07:31.170 --> 01:07:34.080
And in Clara dos Anjos
there is one part --

01:07:34.080 --> 01:07:38.540
