&gt;&gt; So, I'm thinking
about this, she's Clara,

01:10:46.740 --> 01:10:50.380
she's dos Anjos, but she's not.

01:10:50.380 --> 01:10:51.680
So, she's nothing.

01:10:51.680 --> 01:10:52.980
And it's very...

01:10:52.980 --> 01:10:54.280
