for various reasons.

01:14:34.340 --> 01:14:36.530
I'm going to say two of them.

01:14:36.530 --> 01:14:40.510
One of them I gave
you the answer today.

01:14:40.510 --> 01:14:43.260
I wrote -- I'm writing
a lot of assess,

01:14:43.260 --> 01:14:47.840
showing how Brazil is a
very unequal country and how

01:14:47.840 --> 01:14:52.110
in this very unequal
