on the region of Brazil.

01:20:44.150 --> 01:20:46.050
It's completely different.

01:20:46.050 --> 01:20:47.710
If you ask your question

01:20:47.710 --> 01:20:51.540
in the south you will
have one kind of answer.

01:20:51.540 --> 01:20:52.960
If you go to the [inaudible]

01:20:52.960 --> 01:20:57.930
and ask another question you're
going to receive another answer.

01:20:57.930 --> 01:21:01.530
I guess you will not
receive your answer.

01:21:01.530 --> 01:21:05.270
And then if you go to the
center of Brazil, also.

01:21:05.270 --> 01:21:10.080
So, Brazil as the United
States I think it has a form

01:21:10.080 --> 01:21:16.650
of a continent, and the
reality of a continent.

01:21:16.650 --> 01:21:21.120
But even so, if you
go to, for example,

01:21:21.120 --> 01:21:26.140
to a place like [speaking
foreign language],

01:21:26.140 --> 01:21:27.440
I interviewed a [speaking
foreign language],

01:21:27.440 --> 01:21:29.720
I know this person,
this man, [inaudible].

01:21:29.720 --> 01:21:33.900
He wanted to talk with me,
he knew the subject I wanted

01:21:33.900 --> 01:21:36.490
to talk with him and he --

01:21:36.490 --> 01:21:41.500
and eventually when I opened
the door and start talk

01:21:41.500 --> 01:21:47.010
to him he said to me,
"you know, go," you know,

01:21:47.010 --> 01:21:53.350
because in Brazil
you can go or no go,

01:21:53.350 --> 01:21:54.650
[speaking foreign language].

01:21:54.650 --> 01:21:58.510
The moment -- during
the moment I was back,

01:21:58.510 --> 01:21:59.840
